#

Zesty Lemon Waffles

30 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

glutendairyegg

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

breakfastbrunchsweet

Description

Light, fluffy waffles with a refreshing lemon twist, perfect for breakfast or brunch!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 3/4 cups
  • milk: 1 1/2 cups
  • eggs: 2 large
  • unsalted butter: 1/2 cup, melted
  • granulated sugar: 1/4 cup
  • baking powder: 1 tbsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • lemon zest: 2 tbsp
  • lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • powdered sugar: for dusting
